         systemd,
         adduser,
         openssl,
         ca-certificates,
         locales,
         docker.io | docker-ce-cli,
         docker-compose-plugin
Description: doc-store MCP adapter server
 Installs a thin systemd unit that runs the doc-store Docker image and a
 PostgreSQL/pgvector container through docker compose. Host runtime files are
 owned by docstoreuesr:docstoregrp and the same numeric IDs are mapped inside
 the application container.
